|---|---|
| Irish Telecom Overview (2015–2024) | KPI summary, ARPU trends, broadband usage vs subscribers, technology breakdown |
| Technology Shifts: Mobile–Broadband Transition | 2G/3G decline, 4G/5G adoption, landline revenue erosion, broadband revenue overtaking mobile |
| Market Dynamics | Operator market shares (mobile & broadband), fixed vs mobile infrastructure investment |

---



5. ## Data Pipeline

Raw data (ComReg Excel workbook, 2005–2025) → scoped to 2015–2024 for completeness → segregated by metric type (Subscription, Revenue, Traffic, Investment) → pivoted to columnar format → standardised naming conventions → missing value treatment (mean imputation for minor gaps; 5G data excluded pre-Q2 2020) → Time_ID foreign key applied across all tables → imported into Tableau for visualisation.

